	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Why the nesasm.exe the Biggest Bank 127？
<br />And how can translate is bigger ？ <img src="./images/smilies/icon_question.gif" alt=":?:" title="Question" />

		

		</td>
	</tr>
